title: LESSON 1
hint: Collect chips to get past the chip socket. Use keys to open doors.

title: LESSON 2
hint: Push blocks into water to make dirt. Watch out for monsters.

title: LESSON 3
hint: Suction-boots for force floors. Fire boots  for fire. Flippers for water. Skates for ice.

title: LESSON 4
hint: The blue button controls the tanks. The green button toggles walls. Sometimes things are hidden under blocks.

title: LESSON 5
hint: The red button controls the clone machine. The brown button opens traps.

title: LESSON 6
hint: Blue walls may be fake. Some invisible walls never appear. There can be extra chips.

title: LESSON 7
hint: Teleports can be directional. The thief takes your tools. New walls can appear under you.

title: LESSON 8
hint: Monsters are stopped by dirt and gravel.

title: PARANOIA
